{"tid":1066474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵撞車：紅隧、西隧及東隧交通擠塞","createTime":"2019-03-18T02:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T03:27:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"283d6565df6fe6bd5c11cb4e309481fdb1ea6479","tid":1066474,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190318/photo/bkn-20190318092933464-0318_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190318100031\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190318092933464-0318_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190318100031&h=be5f74a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今日(18日)凌晨在荃灣線中環站進行新信號測試，期間發生列車相撞事故，導致荃灣線金鐘至中環站服務全日暫停，不少市民需轉用其他交通工具，至早上返工時間，西隧、東隧及紅隧因使用者增加導致大塞車。 <br />\n<br />\n運輸署亦宣布，因車多關係，觀塘繞道往東區海底隧道方向的交通繁忙，現時車龍已延至九龍灣，敬請忍讓及小心駕駛。另外，紅隧車龍延至公主道，西隧車龍已延至奧海城。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190318/bkn-20190318092933464-0318_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fbkn-20190318092933464-0318_00822_001.html&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=daee5273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190318/bkn-20190318092933464-0318_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d94a328518a019d471b7a1c0c3869edaf2c222e7","tid":1066474,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193b43954c7eb1dbda1aed3b9e56b677a98cafc7","tid":1066474,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"返工唔好遲到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f8e0064f14b8985d5396751ed114d9b23efb4c","tid":1066474,"u